My spirits are very low... I'm going to apply to return

Mi tablet de última generación pero su página va muuuyy lenta. No cargan los cursos y tienes que esperar demasiado tiempo para abrir los cursos que he pagado. Pongan soluciones para el cliente, es una vergüenza que está supuesta academia online de tanto prestigio funcione tan mal y tan lenta.

Tenia una cuenta con muchos cursos comprados y recientemente compre un solo curso en otra localidad por ahorrarme algo de plata y me lo mande como regalo. Resulta que por hacer eso me banean ambas cuentas diciendo que es un abuso de regalo. Ya vi sus condiciones de uso y no detalla nada semejante para tener la razon de banearme permanentemente. Hable con el equipo de udemy y me dijeron que no pueden hacer nada. Solo por $5, enserio?

Had to login to my pc and purchase the course with credits, but anyway Udemy owes me 9,99€ and won't answer me.

Author: CH4W1 HG0

Translated Body: The option to be able to transmit to a Smart TV is missing, I have also noticed that it has a bug, when minimizing the video and opening it again it starts again, that is, it does not save the progress

Author: Leandro Arias
Body: Tengo android y un g60s Motorola y para poder hacer laa descargas en la sd tuve que borrar la app y antes de iniciar ña aplicación configurar los permisos manualmente manteniendo apretado el icono de la app, luego ir a mi perfil y configurar la descarga solo por wifi(viene predeterminada) y que dercargue en sd, y darle reiniciar la app. Así funcionó la descarga de las clases en la sd. Espero que a alguno le sirva.
Translated Body: I have android and a Motorola g60s and to be able to download to the sd I had to delete the app and before starting the application configure the permissions manually by holding down the app icon, then go to my profile and configure the download only by wifi (it comes by default) and download to sd, and restart the app. This is how the download of the classes in the sd worked. I hope someone finds it useful.

Translated Body: I'm lovin 'it. Courses with tremendous quality, a very nice interface. Apart from that there are always offers, and there are instructors there who offer a lot for a low price, and others for free. Thank you for creating this platform.

Author: Darlin Sebastian.
Body: Cuando compras los cursos no te aparecen en la sección de "mi aprendizaje - todos los cursos". El soporte técnico es muy demorado, te pideb cualquier cantidad de informaciones para verificar si la compra la hiciste y finalmente te dicen "entra en contacto con Google play" deben solucionar esta situación.
Translated Body: When you buy the courses they do not appear in the "my learning - all courses" section. The technical support is very slow, they ask you for any amount of information to verify if you made the purchase and finally they tell you "contact Google play" they should solve this situation.

La seguridad no tiene que prioridad ante el acceso a la información. Translated Body: My money has been stolen. Translated Body: With the latest update it tells me that the videos have expired because they exceed 30 days and to download them again despite having done it a few days ago, apart from the functionality of downloading videos does not even serve its purpose, if it consumes the data, despite already be downloaded. The only way to see them is by turning off the data or the network, otherwise it will continue to try to load the video as if it were not downloaded

No sé si más personas les moleste pero a mí simplemente me quitan las ganas totalmente de ver cualquier curso.
Translated Body: I can't take it anymore, this is suffering !! It is impossible to take the courses if every time you pause a video to analyze some detail, the image of playing the video appears. It covers almost the entire part of the video and the worst thing about it is that there is no button or way to remove it. I don't know if more people are bothering them but they just totally take away my desire to see any course.

Author: Avisarme Aqui
Body: La innovación ha muerto. La feature para notas en dispositivos moviles no es mas que un simple input text. Para ser una empresa con millones y no poder tener una feature mas calidad, pues algo esta mal. Si hicieran un estudio, la mayoría de los estudiantes no llegan a terminar los cursos. Eso es culpa del maestro y nosotros damos garantía? Si, pero es ahi donde flaquean, no innovan en análisis dirigido usuario. Tengo una lista de features que he pensado hacer un udemy 2.0 con su misma api.
Translated Body: Innovation is dead. The feature for notes on mobile devices is nothing more than a simple text input. To be a company with millions and not be able to have a more quality feature, because something is wrong. If they do a study, most of the students do not finish the courses. Is that the teacher's fault and we give a guarantee? Yes, but that's where they falter, they don't innovate in user-directed analysis. I have a list of features that I have thought about making a udemy 2.0 with the same api.

La totalidad de sus cursos debería estar su titulado. Así incluyen un grupo importante en sus aprendizajes.

Body: La app no es mala, pero que no se pueda habilitar la opción de chromecast en todos los cursos es un error ENORME en mi opinión ya que se trata de que la accesibilidad al contenido sea la mejor. Que no hayan hecho una app para Xbox y poder ver los videos desde ahí tambien es algo que dificulta la accesibilidad. Si no solucionan esto, yo almenos pruebo otra plataforma que si funcione con chromecast.
Translated Body: The app is not bad, but that the chromecast option cannot be enabled in all courses is a HUGE mistake in my opinion since it is about the accessibility of the content being the best. That they have not made an app for Xbox and being able to see the videos from there is also something that makes accessibility difficult. If they don't solve this, I at least try another platform that works with chromecast.

Whenever an update comes out I download it but they do not solve it and reading the comments I see that I am not the only one with the problem. If you can add a notification above (like Netflix, amazon prime, etc) that says the download process would be great for the content of the courses are good. Greetings

Esto me sucede a diario y es bastante molesto. He desinstalado la app en varias ocasiones pero el problema sigue. Cuando lo solucionen (eso espero) les daré las 5 estrellas. Nota: mi equipo es un A30.
Translated Body: The app is great and I think it is worth 5 stars, if it weren't for the fact that I always log out and to log back in I have to clear the app's data and cache, if not, it won't let me in. This happens to me on a daily basis and it is quite annoying. I have uninstalled the app several times but the problem continues. When they fix it (I hope so) I will give them 5 stars. Note: my equipment is an A30.

Translated Body: Hi! Did they remove the Google play card payment method? I have always bought courses on udemy this way and now after the last update, when wanting to buy a course, I noticed that this method was not found. Pero siento que le faltan más funciones: como diferentes idiomas en los documentos, en las clases y videos. porque uno al leer los subtítulos no le pone cuidado al vídeo como tal. Yo estoy estudiando fotografía pero no sé nada de inglés. Deberían agregar diferentes idiomas para poder elegir (como en este caso Español) Sería bueno que solucionaran eso. Preferencias de idiomas.
Translated Body: In general it is fine, the app serves its purpose. But I feel like it lacks more features: like different languages in documents, in classes, and videos. because one when reading the subtitles does not pay attention to the video as such. I am studying photography but I don't know any English. They should add different languages to be able to choose (like in this case Spanish) It would be good if they solved that. Author: Alejandro Orozco
Body: PÉSIMA APLICACIÓN. EL DÍA DE HOY EN LA MAÑANA compré un curso de cómo pagar impuestos, me hicieron el cobro a la tarjeta, tengo el comprobante de pago de Google y la aplicación sigue sin dejarme entrar al curso. Adicional a eso, su servicio al cliente nunca contesta y no dan solución a este tema. Estaba muy ilusionado de empezar mi curso y con estás mamadas me mataron toda la ilusión.
Translated Body: BAD APPLICATION. TODAY IN THE MORNING I bought a course on how to pay taxes, they charged my card, I have proof of payment from Google and the application still won't let me enter the course. In addition to that, their customer service never answers and they do not provide a solution to this issue. I was very excited to start my course and with these blowjobs they killed all the illusion.

Author: Fernando MT
Body: Hasta ahora no tengo quejas. Mi única petición sería que los links se pudieran abrir desde la aplicación, ya que cuando llega algún correo de algún profesor el link lo abre en el navegador y es un poco incómodo para quien no acostumbra a tener su sesión iniciada en varios sitios. La función que menciono sería algo parecido a cuando sale la opción de elegir con que aplicación abrir un enlace en android.
Translated Body: So far I have no complaints. My only request would be that the links could be opened from the application, since when an email arrives from a teacher the link opens it in the browser and it is a bit uncomfortable for those who do not usually have their session started on several sites. The function that I mention would be something similar to when the option to choose with which application to open a link in android comes out.

Translated Body: The application is not updated. Only the new subscriber or new review messages are skipped, but when you want to see your number of students for each course, a script always appears. And from bad to worse, now it does not load searches in student mode and nothing is displayed in instructor mode. The question is then what is the application for?

Deberian de trabajar en esa parte ya que les aseguro que mi internet funciona perfectamente con otras apps Similares. El precio de los cursos es muy bueno pero aparentemente es con relación a la calidad de la App. Pesimo servicio
Translated Body: The application is good, you can download the classes and watch them offline, view your progress in a good way among other good things. The biggest problem is that it takes horribly long to load a video, sometimes it doesn't even play it and just leaves you waiting. They should work on that part since I assure you that my internet works perfectly with other similar apps. The price of the courses is very good but apparently it is in relation to the quality of the App. Terrible service

Translated Body: The courses are fine, but your system no longer has my account, I uninstalled the application because I did a reset on my cell phone. I want to enter the courses again and now it tells me that there is no registration of my account, if I enter through the Google account. And now how do I get my courses back? It is a scam

Si bien, los certificados son simbólicos, la información de muchos cursos es de calidad por lo que al final de cuentas aprendes cuanto quieres. Lo importante es investigar en más de una opción para mejorar tus habilidades.

Así tantas veces como busques y vuelvas a atrás. Cuando usas el buscador al pones gratis y siguen apareciendo todas las pagas primero. Capaz que esto es a propósito, pero no sé qué sentido tiene poner gratis en el filtro si no filtra lo que querés. Sacando eso la aplicación está muy buena. Edit: funcionó!

Translated Body: You have a few days to make the purchase of a course which I needed at that time, but I did not add the course and if I received the discount (in fact I received my payment notification by mail) for the same, now I need and do the return of my money or give me the option of acquiring a new one, I hope and they indicate me the steps to follow so that they support me with this situation.

Translated Body: When I opened my account here in the app I had prices, but then I opened my account on the pc and the prices both in the app and on the pc went up, I know that the prices here are higher than on the official website, but it doesn't have sense that the price increases if the first thing I opened was the account here on Android, I write the review again so that you understand the problem please

Translated Body: Very bad, the videos play very slow and get too stuck, they say it is our internet, but with other applications and / or videos the same does not happen.

Translated Body: In the last update, there was a downside. When I go to see my courses I get: What will you learn first? Your courses will be saved here. And the list of * Headphones image * Category navigation ------- If you could fix please, before it did not happen ... Then the excellent courses ..

Author: Abraham Castañeda

Translated Body: The quality of the courses is variable, I have been able to get some very good ones that have helped me in my professional growth and the teachers kindly answer my questions, it only has a great but the app, although it has the option to download the sessions to see them In offline mode, I have never been able to see the downloaded videos, although it is marked that the video of that session is downloaded, I cannot see them.

Author: Mayte Martín Abad
Body: Todo bien hasta que termino un curso y no me da la opción de descargar mi certificado desde ningún dispositivo. Ya no sé que más hacer, sabiendo que conozco a gente que lo tiene.
Translated Body: All good until I finish a course and it does not give me the option to download my certificate from any device. I don't know what else to do, knowing that I know people who have it.

Author: Alexis Flores

Translated Body: Very good application. Very useful to take the courses. The download option is fantastic. In fact it is the reason why I downloaded the app. I just didn't like not being able to log in with my Google account. They contacted me and now that's it. I recommend the app

Author: Ignacio
Body: Como es lógico en este tipo de plataformas, la calidad de los cursos es variable con cada instructor, pero en general hasta el momento mi experiencia es buena. Normalmente veo desde la PC pero esta bueno contar con la app para algunos momentos. Lo malo es que cuando transmito a ChromeCast muchas veces no me marca los bloques como completados (no es nada extremo, lo resuelvo después en la PC pero es algo a mejorar).
Translated Body: As is logical in this type of platform, the quality of the courses is variable with each instructor, but in general so far my experience is good. Normally I see from the PC but it is good to have the app for some moments. The bad thing is that when I transmit to ChromeCast many times it does not mark the blocks as completed (it is not extreme, I solve it later on the PC but it is something to improve).

Author: Jorge Daniel Villafañe
Body: Funciona genial. Solo hay mucha gente inútil que no sabe usarla o no actualizan las app para mantenerlas estables ¿ y para que? Para tener memoria y sacarse una selfy 😒😒😒 , no me extraña que no les funcione, comprén una memoria o usen un emulador. Gracias queridos desarrolladores.
Translated Body: It works great. There are only many useless people who do not know how to use it or do not update the apps to keep them stable, and for what? To have memory and take a selfy 😒😒😒, it is not surprising that it does not work for them, buy a memory or use an emulator. Thanks dear developers.

Author: Spartan Ghost
Body: Cuando quiero comprar un curso me sale que mi saldo de google es insuficiente y me muestra una cantidad que no es la que tengo, y que es suficiente para comprar un curso.
Translated Body: When I want to buy a course I get that my google balance is insufficient and shows me an amount that is not what I have, and that is enough to buy a course.

Author: Garcia
Body: Para mí es prácticamente un timo, la mayoría de los cursos valen entre 50 y 100 € pero casualmente justo en el día en el que te metes estan a 10 ( que para un curso que igual no supera las 10 horas y que nadie asegura que no sea una basura yo diría que ya esta bien) y además he visto un curso de astrología, creo que no me hace falta hablar más para que entendáis porque lo llamo timo
Translated Body: For me it is practically a scam, most of the courses are worth between € 50 and € 100 but coincidentally just on the day that you enter they are at 10 (which for a course that does not exceed 10 hours and that nobody assures that it does not it is rubbish I would say that it is already ok) and also I have seen an astrology course, I think I do not need to speak more for you to understand why I call it a scam

Y ahora el precio de los cursos a subido desorbitadamente. El precio de los cursos ahora es 5 o 6 veces mayor que al descargar la app. Un timo vaya.
Translated Body: The first course is done without problems with your certificate and at a reasonable price. I started another one, I finished it and I cannot receive nor can I request a certificate. And now the price of the courses has risen wildly. The price of the courses is now 5 or 6 times higher than when downloading the app. A scam go.

Translated Body: What I don't like about UDEMY. It is missing that they say if it is a course in English because when it comes out it has subtitles and you enter and it is in Spanish and you go to another and it says the same description and it is in English and this confuses

Espero que puedan ayudarme
Translated Body: Today I entered the platform, I indicated that my session had expired and that I had to log in again, so I did and was surprised that the courses I paid for two years ago are no longer in the section of my courses And when I looked them up in the list of available courses it asks me to pay for them again when it is assumed that once you pay you have lifetime access. I hope you can help me

Body: Primero, se necesita mejorar la experiencia de usuario. Para cursos grandes, menús colapsables no estarían nada mal, recorrer a cada rato una página completa no es lo mejor. Una pantalla dedicada a descargas, para ver qué se descarga y qué no, borrar o cancelar los videos. Necesita más trabajo, más pantallas y mejor interfaz, pues es fácil perderse. La carga de los vídeos tarda demasiado, y mayor fluidez así como gestos para minimizar el reproductor, hace falta más trabajo para la aplicación.

Debajo de cada curso me dice el numero de clases descargadas, y no me aparecen las clases descargadas. Voy a las carpetas y ahi estan todos los videos y sibtitulos descargados y no entiendo. La app terminó de consumir todos los datos descargando infinitamente los videos. Gastar dinero en vano, que gran oficio.
Translated Body: What a lousy download system. I spent a lot of money on phone data to download the videos and I don't understand why they are downloaded over and over again. Under each course it tells me the number of downloaded classes, and the downloaded classes do not appear to me. I go to the folders and there are all the downloaded videos and subtitles and I don't understand. The app finished consuming all the data infinitely downloading the videos. Spending money in vain, what a great job.

Author: Rodrigo Patiño
Body: Me gusta muchísimo Udemy, pero la aplicación es terrible. A pesar de que la aplicación me deja descargar videos de los cursos directamente a la SD del teléfono, cuando estoy viendo el contenido descargado sólo me deja reproducir 1 video, cuando este termina y comienza el siguiente la aplicación se detiene, el video no se reproduce, incluso si reinicio la aplicación y selecciono el video que quiero manualmente este no se reproduce debido a que no hay conexión a internet (A pesar que lo tengo descargado). Al ver videos descargados el progreso de mi curso de reinicia a 0 - Xiaomi Redmi Note 8 - Android 9 Es muy importante para mi que se solucione este problema de la reproducción de videos, ya que es por lo único que tengo la aplicación en el teléfono.
Translated Body: I really like Udemy, but the application is terrible. Although the application lets me download videos of the courses directly to the SD of the phone, when I am watching the downloaded content it only allows me to play 1 video, when it ends and the next one the application stops, the video does not play , even if I restart the application and select the video I want manually it does not play because there is no internet connection (Although I have downloaded it). When watching downloaded videos the progress of my course of reset to 0 - Xiaomi Redmi Note 8 - Android 9 It is very important for me to solve this problem of video playback, since it is the only thing I have the application on the phone .

Es algo ilógico, les recomiendo tomar un curso de los que venden y solucionen ese error.
Translated Body: It is unfortunate that a technical team of a programming course platform offers a solution to uninstall and install again to view the downloaded courses offline. The solution works, but since last year it has this problem and I already had 13 GB downloaded, I have to download this content again. It is illogical, I recommend taking a course of those who sell and solve that error.

Body: Estaba extasiado ante su app, hasta esta semana. Compré un curso y lo descargué para tomarlo en mi trabajo, donde no tengo internet. Se supone que la función de descargar es no usar internet. No obstante, sin internet intenta cargar las clases que ya tomaste y de las que eliminaste descarga, y al no haber internet, ya no te deja seleccionar la clase que sigue y la clase se pasma. Si esto sigue así, voy a tener que eliminar la app con la consiguiente pérdida de dinero. Estoy muy frustrado.
Translated Body: He was ecstatic about his app, until this week. I bought a course and downloaded it to take it in my work, where I don't have internet. The download function is supposed to be not using the internet. However, without the internet, try to load the classes you have already taken and from which you have downloaded download, and since there is no internet, it no longer lets you select the class that follows and the class is stunned. If this continues, I will have to delete the app with the consequent loss of money. I am very frustrated.

Body: Los cursos son excelentes, no hay queja alguna al respecto. Pero la app tiene que ser mejorada y mucho. Empezando por qué aunque descargues lecciones para no usar datos, está indica que no se puede reproducir sin conexion. La segunda molestia es por el registro de avance del curso, he estado tomando mis lecciones y de un día para otro mi porcentaje de avance ha retrocedido, ¿Cómo es posible pasar de un 40% de avance a solo tener un 3%?. Espero se corrijan estos errores pronto.
Translated Body: The courses are excellent, there is no complaint about it. But the app has to be improved a lot. Starting with why even if you download lessons to not use data, it is indicated that it cannot be played offline. The second nuisance is the registration of progress of the course, I have been taking my lessons and from one day to another my progress percentage has fallen, how is it possible to go from a 40% progress to only have a 3%? I hope these errors are corrected soon.

Cuando hay ofertas (el 95% del tiempo) quitan de la lista los gratuitos. No hay garantias de que el curso de pago sirva, aunque al menos la devolución es de 30 dias...
Translated Body: The application does not work offline, it is absurd to "download" if really what I did was not simply create a blob without real content, it is meaningless. When there are offers (95% of the time) they remove the free ones from the list. There is no guarantee that the payment course will work, although at least the return is 30 days ...

Author: Zenia Calderón Laguardia
Body: Excelentes los cursos, la aplicación es mala, una vez que comienzo a ver los videos se quedan pausados y no descargan, esto me ha generado una gran pérdida de tiempo para mis horas de estudio. He tratado de darle solución a este problema primeramente limpiando la memoria caché del dispositivo y descargando individualmente cada uno de los videos, fue en vano, por último desinstale la aplicación y la instalé nuevamente, pero el problema persiste.
Translated Body: Excellent courses, the application is bad, once I start watching the videos they remain paused and do not download, this has generated a great loss of time for my study hours. I tried to solve this problem first by cleaning the cache of the device and downloading each of the videos individually, it was in vain, finally I uninstalled the application and installed it again, but the problem persists.

Body: Excelente! Mi actual casa de estudios online! Lastima que no puedo acceder a los mejores cursos ya que no poseo los medios, sin embargo es un herramienta que me acerca más a cumplir mi sueño de ser un programador! Estoy iniciando, con el propósito de ser un Desarrollador Full Stack, pero empezaré con el Front-end! Que genial sería poder tener acceso a lo mejor de su contenido! Pero dejando de lado mi situación económica, la App es simplemente espléndida! Gracias por su trabajo!
Translated Body: Excellent! My current house of studies online! Too bad I can't access the best courses since I don't have the means, however it is a tool that brings me closer to fulfilling my dream of being a programmer! I am starting, with the purpose of being a Full Stack Developer, but I will start with the Front-end! How great it would be to have access to the best of your content! But leaving aside my economic situation, the App is simply splendid! Thanks for your job!

No obstante, mi enfado tiene orígen en que a la que lo usas un par de veces, los cursos de 10.99€ pasan a valer 200€ solo para ti: en navegación privada o a mis compañeros de trabajo les sigue saliendo el precio de 10.99€. Si te logueas, te sube los precios justo a la hora de pagar. Me siento muy estafado. Respuesta a Udemy: los precios para mi cuenta son los mismos en la app y en la web. Subiis los precios a algunas cuentas...

Body: No sé pueden calificar los cursos desde el app para Android luego de terminarlos. En ocasiones desde una red WiFi en dónde Youtube o cualquier otra aplicación de vídeo funcionan fluidamente, en el app de Udemy el vídeo se detiene y se queda cargando por mucho tiempo aún cuando se elige una resolución de vídeo baja (360p por ejemplo). Algunos cursos no incluyen ningún recurso adicional como un PDF con el resumen de la clase o la presentación utilizada por el instructor.
